{"tid":2254560,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[警世] GOBUYSHIP集運詐騙黑店私呑貨品無下文","createTime":"2020-10-23T02:28:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T06:27:46.000Z","uid":14409,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ba9b348cf641d03b070721c3937004075a172d07","tid":2254560,"uid":14409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T02:28:55.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><a href=\"https://www.gobuyship.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gobuyship.com&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRC8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=22934d6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gobuyship.com</a><br />\n<br />\n話說之前諗住試吓一間新集運公司，點知試著一間<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">黑店詐騙公司GOBUYSHIP</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n其實佢稱不上喺間集運公司，<span class=\"large\">因為你永遠都唔會收到件貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n同其他苦主討論之後，呢間詐騙公司嘅運作模式大約係:<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"violet\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">客人落咗單&gt;件貨到咗集運倉&gt;聲稱話搵唔到件貨&gt;CS長期潛水&gt;無下文</span></strong></span><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">咁間詐騙公司就可以名正言順食咗件貨</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"blue\">呢間鳩野聲稱全球都有好多個倉，最搞笑嘅係無論你用佢邊個地方嘅倉，佢都會話每一個倉都搵唔到啲貨，喂詐騙公司，你個倉係咪空㗎？乜柒都揾唔到嘅？ </span></span><br />\n<br />\n無聊之後睇吓佢Facebook？ 嘩發現全部都係追數留言呀，個鳩CS仲可以hea覆扮冇事發生過喎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ya3mtKZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYa3mtKZ.jpg&h=90f2eb23&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PsMLaYk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPsMLaYk.jpg&h=6a4076b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大家想經歷下以下情況，就搵呢間詐騙公司㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">1. CS長期潛水，幾日應得你一句，一句搵唔到就當冇事發生過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 平平哋嘅貨等返半年左右就到㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 貴少少嘅貨已經俾呢間野私吞咗啦，呢世都唔會收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.CS會將個責任推比原店舖，有晒Tracking都可以話佢從來冇寄過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. CS會將個責任推比客人，叫佢哋自己搵返運輸公司問吓件貨係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個客服WhatsApp已經三日冇覆過我啦，我都預咗件貨憑空消失㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喺呢邊提醒返大家試新集運公司之前要起一起底先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"violet\"><span class=\"x-large\">見到而家有啲IGshop同黃店都有用GOBUYSHIP嘅自取點，呢邊建議返即時同呢間詐騙公司終止合作，如果唔係你啲貨一樣會憑空消失㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"ca65521e8464690a0bb135185b162bd7032e1ff0","tid":2254560,"uid":14409,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T02:30:06.000Z","msg":"GoBuyShip GBS永不錄用<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1873594\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1873594</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n之前已經有大量苦主<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己衰on9冇起底就用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c987ad3c8a25a7fc782a33241ccf5f14bc3232c6","tid":2254560,"uid":14409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T02:30:37.000Z","msg":"有冇其他人有一樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6073f4e3d3095229ee1dc8c20a168526b62bd753","tid":2254560,"uid":14409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T02:31:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6410dd8a4ee4ad0a51cf1fdb5553d91f65751bd1","tid":2254560,"uid":14409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci